{"tid":760112,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼兔仔咬籠子？🐰🐰😊","createTime":"2018-07-29T08:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T04:04:20.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19515ddbebbb8297f652a080477cd37ac1e2ce7c","tid":760112,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子咬籠其實是想引主人注意，告訴主人牠想出來玩、出來探索。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GZZCdCLIKo&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f6510053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養兔仔：<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=62d6eee8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2d4e921a\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a></span>"},{"pid":"7ec0ffe1645b09102018a5dcaa2206b4d519408c","tid":760112,"uid":120462,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"660787cfb864ddc3186b71ca1772af3bb46a9159","tid":760112,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19515ddbebbb8297f652a080477cd37ac1e2ce7c","tid":760112,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子咬籠其實是想引主人注意，告訴主人牠想出來玩、出來探索。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GZZCdCLIKo&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f6510053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養兔仔：<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=62d6eee8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2d4e921a\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子會不會叫？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子會叫的。不滿的時候會咕咕叫。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predatory animals)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。 <br />\n<br />\n以下video 可以看到兔仔咕咕叫。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸: <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4379e615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更多關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒）：<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f51d2ca3\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a><br />\n<strong>領養兔仔：</strong> <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=62d6eee8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n兔子深入資訊：[url]<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=CYqstLau4GTSc8F2TWgU0PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2d4e921a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> [/url]</span>"},{"pid":"e0